  ---
import { GitForkIcon } from '../../assets/inteldata';
import { AdvertisingIcon, ScalabilityIcon, SmartNotificationIcon, ImpactIcon } from '../../assets/marketing-icons';
---
<section id="mmi" class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-base text-black font-bold tracking-wide uppercase mb-2">Marketing estratégico</h2>
        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-black mb-4">Motor de Marketing Inteligente</p>
        <p class="text-2xl text-gray-600">Potencia tu negocio con datos reales y automatización</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1: Main Core (Large) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-3 bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 border border-gray-100 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/30 transition-all group relative">
          <GitForkIcon client:visible size={32} className="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-[#333] p-2 rounded-2xl text-primary" />
          <div>
            
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Inteligencia de Datos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              CarniApp mantiene un <strong>registro y perfil detallado de tus clientes</strong>. Infiere comportamientos, anticipa necesidades y hace que tus acciones de marketing sean precisas.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8">
             <div class="h-2 w-full bg-gray-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
               <div class="h-full bg-blue-500 w-3/4 rounded-full"></div>
             </div>
             <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mt-2 text-right">Análisis en tiempo real</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Social Media -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-3 bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/30 transition-all group relative">
            <AdvertisingIcon client:visible size={32} className="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-[#333] p-2 rounded-2xl text-primary" />
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Publicidad Eficiente</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Tu inversión publicitaria en redes sociales se diluye cuando una persona muestra interés en carne. Recibe tu publicidad y la de tu competencia, pero con CarniApp <strong>llegas directo</strong>.
            </p>
            <!-- <div class="flex gap-2">
               <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Facebook Ads</span>
               <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Instagram</span>
            </div> -->
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Growth -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/30 transition-all group relative">
          <ScalabilityIcon client:visible size={26} className="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-[#333] p-2 rounded-2xl text-primary" />
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-2">Escalabilidad</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
             Ayuda a escalar ventas, segmentar público y elaborar estrategias apoyadas en <strong>datos verdaderos</strong> de propia recopilación.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4: Notifications -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/30 transition-all group relative">
          <SmartNotificationIcon client:visible size={26} className="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-[#333] p-2 rounded-2xl text-primary" />
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-2">Notificaciones Smart</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
             Recomendaciones dirigidas por interés, función del clima y comportamiento del cliente.
          </p>
        </div>

         <!-- Card 5: Result -->
         <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-dark p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 border border-gray-800 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/30 transition-all text-white flex flex-col justify-center text-center group relative">
           <ImpactIcon client:visible size={26} className="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-[#333] p-2 rounded-2xl text-primary" />
           <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-1">Impacto Total</h3>
           <p class="text-lg">Efectividad y eficiencia máxima.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
